name: Flowers I saw in those days 03
description:
They were there, and I saw them.
In memory of those days.
2018
Version: 03/09
------------------------------------------------------------
Flowers I saw in those days is a series about those flowers I saw in those tough days. 
During the time, those flowers were set in front of the door of my living place, every time I came back and saw them in the dark, so I took my film camera and shoot them.
